# ── Secrets — NEVER commit ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Track only startup.template.md (the secret-free setup wizard). Any local,
# filled-in copy (startup.md / startup.local.md) may hold the one-time SSH
# password and stays private.
startup.md
startup.local.md
*.pass
*_secrets*
*.pem
id_ed25519*
id_rsa*

# Campaign state — each box is its own nested git repo, never in the public repo
boxes/

# Release artifacts — built from `git archive`, regenerable, never committed
crucible-*.zip
/dist/

# Local one-off prompts / bundles (may contain host details — never publish)
crucible_cleanup_prompt.md
crucible.tar.gz
_tb/

# Python / scratch
__pycache__/
*.pyc

